 # Setup a new program install

 Start by creating a folder under documents we will use 1 folder per program
 Run the following commands
 
 WINEARCH=win32(only rarely use win64) WINEPREFIX=location_of_bottle winetricks
 
 ie: WINEARCH=win32  WINEPREFIX=~/Documents/Wine/testbottle winetricks

 From fonts install corefont and tuhuma
 
 # Running a program
 
 Copy exe in to c drive root of location_of_bottle
 
 WINEARCH=win32  WINEPREFIX=~/Documents/Wine/testbottle wine ~/Documents/Wine/testbottle/drive_c/Sopas/SopasET.exe 
 
 
